                            <div id="collapse18" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading18">
                                <div class="panel-body">
                                    <p>COLLAR allows you to find work easily and flexibly while retaining your independence and your own work-lifestyle balance.  You can work with Buyers all over the world, network and develop a client base that spans geographies and industries which would otherwise would be extremely costly and difficult.</p>
                                    <p>We offer email support  and a vibrant community that makes you feel at home!</p>
                                </div>
